# Volunteering vocabulary

## Namespaces
### Ontology Base URI
prefix :                <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/>

### Core W3C ontologies (OWL 2 reserved vocabulary)
prefix rdf:             <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
prefix rdfs:            <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
prefix owl:             <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
prefix xsd:             <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>

### Other namespaces used
prefix dc:              <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
prefix skos:            <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>
prefix time:            <http://www.w3.org/2006/time#>
prefix vcard:           <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#>
prefix vann:            <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/>


## Taxonomy Class
:Taxonomy
    a skos:ConceptScheme ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    skos:hasTopConcept :Accessibility, :Cause, :Requirement, :Reward, :Skill ;
    dc:title "Volunteering Taxonomy"@en ;
    dc:description "The taxonomy of concepts related to volunteering activities."@en ;
    rdfs:label "Taxonomy"@en ;
.

:Concept
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subClassOf skos:Concept ;
    dc:description "Volunteering Concept"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Any concept related to volunteering activities."@en ;
    rdfs:label "Concept"@en ;
.


### Object Properties
:relatedConcept
    a owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:range :Concept ;
    rdfs:label "has related concept"@en ;
.

:accessibility
    a owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subPropertyOf :relatedConcept ;
    rdfs:label "has accessibility information"@en ;
.

:requirement
    a owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subPropertyOf :relatedConcept ;
    rdfs:label "has requirement"@en ;
.

:skill
    a owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subPropertyOf :relatedConcept ;
    rdfs:label "has skill"@en ;
.


### Object Properties
:Accessibility
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subClassOf :Concept ;
    :conceptLabel "Accessibility"@en ;
    :description "Any accessibility information related to volunteering activities."@en ;
.

:Cause
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subClassOf :Concept ;
    :conceptLabel "Charitable Cause"@en ;
    :description "Any charitable cause related to volunteering activities."@en ;
.

:Requirement
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subClassOf :Concept ;
    :conceptLabel "Requirement"@en ;
    :description "Any requirement related to volunteering activities."@en ;
.

:Reward
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subClassOf :Concept ;
    :conceptLabel "Reward"@en ;
    :description "Any reward related to volunteering activities."@en ;
.

:Skill
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subClassOf :Concept ;
    :conceptLabel "Skill"@en ;
    :description "Any skill related to volunteering activities."@en ;
.
